\par }\pard \sl240\slmult0\widctlpar\tx1440 {\b\f2 Indicator\tab Description}{\f2 
\par }\pard \fi-1440\li1440\sa120\widctlpar\tx1440 {\f2 ??x??\tab Character dimensions of the screen
\par UNLOCK or LOCK\tab Shows whether the screen is locked to prevent resizing.
\par INS or OVR\tab Text insertion mode is selected, or overstrike mode is selected
\par }\pard \fi-1440\li1440\sa120\sl240\slmult0\widctlpar\tx1440 {\f2 CAP\tab The Caps Lock key is latched down.
