\par }\pard \sl240\slmult0\widctlpar {\f2 It is the goal of the author to make WinFrotz fully Z-Machine compliant; that is, make it able to run all versions of Z-Machine code.  As of this writing WinFrotz can run }{\b\f2 all}{\f2 
